    "# OpenEnv Email Triage - Final Colab T4 Notebook\n",
    "\n",
    "Use this on **Google Colab Free Tier T4 GPU**.\n",
    "\n",
    "Important:\n",
    "- run shell commands in `!` cells\n",
    "- run Python `print(...)` in normal Python cells\n",
    "- do **not** mix both in one cell"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
